@sivy great to hear it!

So, looking quickly at your outline, I think that should absolutely work with the new system.  Just make sure that `internal_chat_plugins` is a python module, and the one you specify in `config.py`.  You'll be all set.  You could also group those plugins into submodules, and still have it be fine, but you'd need to split your templates into the submodules as well.

It might be worth a look at the [`MODULE_DESCRIPTION` stuff](http://skoczen.github.io/will/plugins/create/#what-about-that-awesome-help-text) that does the grouping for help text.  A lot of people have found it to be a useful principle for organizing things.

